  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/35e6d62b5b5f6f66d973ceed21e86a5a.poster.avif?t=1771586818\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/35e6d62b5b5f6f66d973ceed21e86a5a.webm?t=1771586818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/35e6d62b5b5f6f66d973ceed21e86a5a.mp4?t=1771586818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sprout Valley is a laid-back, cozy farming sim where you build and create the cuddly island homestead of your dreams. Enjoy a captivatingly sweet story with over 20 hours of content, set in a world full of charm and warmth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/f8163c8faca4b0aa5937bb33bd4bed9a.avif?t=1771586818\" width=1560 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/858f54ef73dd4fc0dbc21a64a4be3f50.poster.avif?t=1771586818\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/858f54ef73dd4fc0dbc21a64a4be3f50.webm?t=1771586818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/858f54ef73dd4fc0dbc21a64a4be3f50.mp4?t=1771586818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Nico, an adorable cat on a journey to turn the peaceful island archipelago of Ostara into a place to call home. Along the way, Nico will make new friends, experience heartfelt moments, and uncover the many little secrets hidden across Ostara.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/604a2f856ae7fc0c1214c7ee2d68395b.avif?t=1771586818\" width=1560 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/5b59f4c48fef3ae8260b968a544a5223.poster.avif?t=1771586818\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/5b59f4c48fef3ae8260b968a544a5223.webm?t=1771586818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/5b59f4c48fef3ae8260b968a544a5223.mp4?t=1771586818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedurally generated islands across four unique biomes offer endless variety and plenty to do. Grow crops, harvest plants, care for animals, mine precious resources, forage for goodies, buy and sell your wares, decorate your home, go fishing, or simply head out and explore at your own pace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/ab3b0e3969985581aa1e796d0ab5483e.avif?t=1771586818\" width=1560 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/297c602c75a8d31f6b687dec759986cb.poster.avif?t=1771586818\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/297c602c75a8d31f6b687dec759986cb.webm?t=1771586818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/297c602c75a8d31f6b687dec759986cb.mp4?t=1771586818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A dynamic weather system and day–night cycle create unique in-game events, making each passing day feel alive and natural.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/ff3438793787ab9e2b5918a3273ad219.avif?t=1771586818\" width=1560 height=146 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Connect and transform multiple plots of land into a sprawling island farm</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend your days farming, mining, foraging, crafting, fishing, or just exploring</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock, craft, or purchase a variety of items to customize and decorate your home</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nurture and care for cuddly farm critters and household pets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel to other islands and explore four distinct biomes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience dynamic events tied to weather and the day–night cycle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize Nico with a variety of fun outfits</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy charming dialogue and a heartfelt story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 20 hours of story content</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/08cc8c9fba8bea7b51cea4b082acbed6.poster.avif?t=1771586818\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/08cc8c9fba8bea7b51cea4b082acbed6.webm?t=1771586818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/08cc8c9fba8bea7b51cea4b082acbed6.mp4?t=1771586818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/35e6d62b5b5f6f66d973ceed21e86a5a.poster.avif?t=1771586818\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/35e6d62b5b5f6f66d973ceed21e86a5a.webm?t=1771586818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/35e6d62b5b5f6f66d973ceed21e86a5a.mp4?t=1771586818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sprout Valley is a laid-back, cozy farming sim where you build and create the cuddly island homestead of your dreams. Enjoy a captivatingly sweet story with over 20 hours of content, set in a world full of charm and warmth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/f8163c8faca4b0aa5937bb33bd4bed9a.avif?t=1771586818\" width=1560 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/858f54ef73dd4fc0dbc21a64a4be3f50.poster.avif?t=1771586818\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/858f54ef73dd4fc0dbc21a64a4be3f50.webm?t=1771586818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/858f54ef73dd4fc0dbc21a64a4be3f50.mp4?t=1771586818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Nico, an adorable cat on a journey to turn the peaceful island archipelago of Ostara into a place to call home. Along the way, Nico will make new friends, experience heartfelt moments, and uncover the many little secrets hidden across Ostara.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/604a2f856ae7fc0c1214c7ee2d68395b.avif?t=1771586818\" width=1560 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/5b59f4c48fef3ae8260b968a544a5223.poster.avif?t=1771586818\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/5b59f4c48fef3ae8260b968a544a5223.webm?t=1771586818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/5b59f4c48fef3ae8260b968a544a5223.mp4?t=1771586818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedurally generated islands across four unique biomes offer endless variety and plenty to do. Grow crops, harvest plants, care for animals, mine precious resources, forage for goodies, buy and sell your wares, decorate your home, go fishing, or simply head out and explore at your own pace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/ab3b0e3969985581aa1e796d0ab5483e.avif?t=1771586818\" width=1560 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/297c602c75a8d31f6b687dec759986cb.poster.avif?t=1771586818\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/297c602c75a8d31f6b687dec759986cb.webm?t=1771586818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/297c602c75a8d31f6b687dec759986cb.mp4?t=1771586818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A dynamic weather system and day–night cycle create unique in-game events, making each passing day feel alive and natural.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/ff3438793787ab9e2b5918a3273ad219.avif?t=1771586818\" width=1560 height=146 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Connect and transform multiple plots of land into a sprawling island farm</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend your days farming, mining, foraging, crafting, fishing, or just exploring</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock, craft, or purchase a variety of items to customize and decorate your home</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nurture and care for cuddly farm critters and household pets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel to other islands and explore four distinct biomes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience dynamic events tied to weather and the day–night cycle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize Nico with a variety of fun outfits</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy charming dialogue and a heartfelt story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 20 hours of story content</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964820/extras/08cc8c9fba8bea7b51cea4b082acbed6.poster.avif?t=1771586818\" width=1170 height